    <briefdescription>
<para>System for binding score values to UI text components. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Queries entities with ScoreObserverComponent, NumberFormatterComponent, and UiTextComponent. When the score observer signals an update, the formatted total score is propagated to the text component for display.</para>
